This paper deals with the design of a data structure for answering distance queries in graphs, which is a fundamental problem in computer science. The paper presents an algorithmic solution to this problem, which is likely to be of interest to researchers in the areas of data structures (cs.DS), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), computational geometry (cs.CG), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
